gamerules.gamerules2: Base Game is a 1 Line Game
gamerules.highestWin: Only the highest win pays perline
gamerules.Bonus_Re-spin_Rule: If Reel 1 and Reel 2 have the same symbol the third reel will have the power chance re-spin feature. Only the third reel will spin again randomly once out of 5 spins to enhance the winning chances
